metadata.title: RZ/V: Free AI Applications for Mass Production Use

sections.content:
Question:
Can the free AI application be used for mass production?
Answer:
Available for use.
However, no compensation for mass production will be provided.
Please use at customer own risk after evaluation.
Suitable Products
RZ/V
